    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, kept it garage-parked, and it's sparkling inside and out. No scratches, no dents, just pure driving perfection. You won't find another one this clean! Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
