    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, a definitive example of high-performance JDM engineering. This chassis retains its factory 50:50 weight distribution and features the 13B-REW twin-rotor powerplant, delivering seamless power through its complex sequential twin-turbocharger system. The powertrain is in peak mechanical health, with verified high compression across all rotor faces and a cooling system free of thermal degradation. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise five-speed manual gearbox and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque transfer. Every suspension component, from the aluminum double-wishbones to the bushings, remains taut and responsive. This vehicle is completely stock, exhibiting no vacuum leaks or modifications, and the exterior retains its original factory finish with zero oxidation. For the discerning enthusiast seeking a turn-key, museum-quality FD, this specimen is unrivaled.",
